messages.messageBody:
In a message dated 1/4/2003 1:29:03 PM Eastern Standard Time,
kellitraas@... writes:


> We were driving all over looking for that game last week, I'll have to look
> closer at it, I have no idea what Woodward is?!
>
> Kelli
>

Woodward camp. It's a camp that specializes in skateboarding, BMX/biking, and
rollerblading. They also have a gymnastics camp. All in the beautiful Penn's
Valley. Indoor and outdoor parks. Pool, horseback riding, you name it.

My 'puter's slow or I'd give you the site. Plug in "Woodward skateboard" in
Google; you'll get it.

~Kelly
